     Log'StartupSession Finished'
     secs‚Üê1000√∑‚ç®¬Ø2-/11 ‚éïDT{‚äÉ‚åΩ'T-,:.'‚éïVFI‚äÉ'‚îÄ'‚àò‚âÝ‚çõ‚äÜ‚çµ}¬®log
     shell‚Üê2‚äÉsecs
     tasks‚Üê' ‚îÄ (.*)'‚éïS' seconds \1'‚ä¢¬Ø1‚Üìlog
     (secs tasks)/‚ç®‚Üê‚äÇ2‚âÝ‚ç≥‚â¢tasks
     secs,‚Üê+/secs ‚ãÑ tasks,‚Üê‚äÇ' SECONDS IN TOTAL (excluding',(2‚çïshell),' seconds for fetching process start time)'
     :If ‚àÜSYSTEM.Executable.Unicode
         bars‚Üê‚Üë(,‚àò√ó‚éïUCS‚ç§‚åø9608+0,8-‚ä¢)‚åø0 8‚ä§‚åä0.5+8√ósecs
     :Else
         bars‚Üê/‚àò'‚éï'‚ç§0‚åä0.5+secs
     :EndIf
     times‚Üê'=== %ISO%.fff"Z" ==='‚àÜDT 1 ‚éïDT'Z'
     times,‚Üê‚äÇ‚éïJSON ‚éïOPT'Dialect' 'JSON5'‚ä¢‚àÜSYSTEM.Executable
     times,‚Üêtasks,¬®‚ç®‚Üìbars,2‚çï‚ç™secs
     times‚äÇ‚çõ‚éïNPUT dsr 2
 :EndIf
